Title : Flatmates Bill
Description: An app that gets as input the amount of a bill for a particular period and the days that each of the flatmates stayed in house for that period and returns how much each flatmates needs to pay. It generates a pdf report
stating the names, cost, and period.
Objects: Bill:
            amount
            period
         Flatmates:
            days_in_house
            name_of_flatmate
            pays(bill)
         PDF Report:
            filename
            generate(flatmate1,flatemate2,bill)
            

